<bibRefCitation author="Burns" box="[151,377,223,248]" pageId="6" pageNumber="299" refString="Burns, K. J., Unitt, P. &amp; Mason, N. A. (2016) A genus-level classification of the family Thraupidae (Class Aves: Order Passeriformes). Zootaxa, 4088 (3), 329 - 354." type="journal article" year="2016">
Burns 
<emphasis box="[234,300,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="299">et al.</emphasis>
2016
</bibRefCitation>
): 
